(ringtone playing)

19:10.983 --> 19:12.609
Unbelievable.

19:13.777 --> 19:15.237
Hi, Christy.

19:15.320 --> 19:17.406
No. I'm up.

19:17.489 --> 19:18.574
How's it going, honey?

